            },
            {
                "question": "Does the server do resets/wipes?",
                "answer": "<p>We perform a full server wipe every New Year’s Day. Previous worlds are archived and made available for players to download and use locally.<br><br>The Nether and The End receive an additional wipe in mid-summer.</p>"
